>
  <section class="legal">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms and Conditions of Use</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        This website is dedicated to the presentation and online sale of original artworks created by
        the artist Layla Lastra.
      </p>
      <p>
        Accessing and using this website implies full acceptance of these Terms and Conditions.
      </p>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Use of the website</h2>
        <p>
          Users agree to use this website lawfully and respectfully. Any illegal or harmful use is
          strictly prohibited.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>
          All artworks, images, texts, and content are the exclusive property of Layla Lastra. Any
          reproduction or use without written permission is prohibited.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Liability</h2>
        <p>
          Information is provided in good faith. Layla Lastra does not guarantee the absence of errors.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Modifications</h2>
        <p>
          Layla Lastra reserves the right to modify these terms at any time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: #faf8f6;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .lead {
    text-align: center;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #e8e5e0;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
